OL,3,CPaw-litics in action: Dogs
OL,4,Cphotographed outside polling stations
OL,6,FIt's election day in parts of England,
OL,7,FScotland, and Wales, and as the
OL,8,Fcountry heads to the polls, political
OL,9,Fleaders have been photographed in
OL,10,Ftheir own constituencies casting their
OL,11,Fvotes.
OL,13,FKeir Starmer and his wife Victoria,
OL,14,Fcast their votes at Westminster Chapel
OL,15,Fin central London on Thursday morning.
OL,17,FLib Dem leader Ed Davey and his wife
OL,18,FEmily cast their votes at Surbiton
OL,19,FHill Methodist Church in south-west
OL,20,FLondon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
