OL,3,CPaw-litics in action: Dogs
OL,4,Cphotographed outside polling stations
OL,6,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch and
OL,7,Fher husband Hamish cast their votes at
OL,8,FClavering Village Hall in Saffron
OL,9,FWalden.
OL,11,FReform UK's Nigel Farage cast his vote
OL,12,Fin Walton-on-the-Naze, Essex.
OL,14,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski cast
OL,15,Fhis own ballot by post and accompanied
OL,16,Fthe Welsh Green leader Anthony
OL,17,FSlaughter to his polling station in
OL,18,FPenarth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
