OL,3,CPaw-litics in action: Dogs
OL,4,Cphotographed outside polling stations
OL,6,FParty leaders weren't the only ones
OL,7,Fpictured heading to the polling
OL,8,Fstation as the election tradition of
OL,9,Fdogs at polling stations continued
OL,10,Facross the country.
OL,12,FThe trend of photographing dogs at
OL,13,Fpolling stations has grown in recent
OL,14,Fyears, with the accompanying hashtag
OL,15,Fand internet acclaim.
OL,17,FMost polling stations do not allow
OL,18,Fdogs inside to avoid disrupting voters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
