OL,3,CPaw-litics in action: Dogs
OL,4,Cphotographed outside polling stations
OL,6,FAdditionally, photography inside
OL,7,Fpolling stations is prohibited to
OL,8,Favoid unintentionally exposing
OL,9,Fsomeone's ballot, a crime that could
OL,10,Fresult in a fine of up to #5,000 or
OL,11,Fsix months in prison.
OL,13,FThe photos outside voting stations are
OL,14,Foften picked up by broadcasters who
OL,15,Fare restricted by what they can and
OL,16,Fcan't say on polling day and welcome
OL,17,Fthe picture as a way of reporting the
OL,18,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
