OL,3,CPaw-litics in action: Dogs
OL,4,Cphotographed outside polling stations
OL,6,FPolitical leaders have also got in on
OL,7,Fthe action, with former PM Boris
OL,8,FJohnson taking his dog Dilyn, and the
OL,9,Fcurrent Mayor of London, Sadiq Khan's
OL,10,FLuna, regularly making appearances.
OL,12,FRead on to see just some of the 2026
OL,13,Felections' dogs at polling station
OL,14,Fphotos.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
